[section#assertions
    [:en] Assertions
]

[para]
[:en]
The header [`<cassert>], described in (Table [#tab:diagnostics.hdr.cassert]),
provides a macro for documenting [=Cpp] program assertions and a mechanism
for disabling the assertion checks.

[table:listing#tab:diagnostics.hdr.cassert
    [:en] Header [`<cassert>] synopsis
    [columns
        [column@headercenter@code
            [:en] Type
        ]
        [column@headercenter@code
            [:en] Name(s)
        ]
    ]
    [border:group@both]
]
[-]
[|] [=Macro]

[|] assert
[table:end]

[para]
[:en] The contents are the same as the Standard C library header [`<assert.h>].

[para:xref]
[:en] ISO C 7.2.
